OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fheavy rain across Orkney this evening
OL,7,Fand strong winds. Shetland starts
OL,8,Fdrier with bright spells, then cloud
OL,9,Fthickens as rain arrives overnight,
OL,10,Fbecoming patchy later for all areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloud and rain initially,
OL,13,Fheavier over Shetland. Mix of brighter
OL,14,Fspells and light showers reaching all
OL,15,Flate morning. Showers building during
OL,16,Fafternoon, perhaps merging to longer
OL,17,Fperiods rain late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
