OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fcloudy start with showers on Saturday
OL,7,Fbefore turning drier with bright
OL,8,Fspells developing. Sunday and Monday
OL,9,Fwill be dry with sunny spells. Breezy
OL,10,FSaturday then winds easing.
